  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><strong style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Step-3.5-Flash</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"1322\" data-imgfileid=\"100017875\" data-ratio=\"0.825925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7d1434dd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8szmUKA3vvjWgic28s2SIykNTeiaCa2z5s1vkHiaUsbQ1y0q3iaVmGQtEQ157PgoGpoicYiaEKeiatoybw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Step-3.5-Flash是由stepfun-ai推出的高性能大语言模型系列，旨在平衡强大的模型能力与多样化的部署需求。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该系列包含199B参数基础版本及FP8、Int4量化优化变体，通过针对性的模型压缩与效率优化技术，在保留核心性能的前提下，有效降低了部署阶段的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">算力与存储开销</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。模型近期完成更新迭代，能够灵活适配不同硬件环境，为自然语言理解、生成等各类任务提供高效、可靠的技术支撑，兼顾了大规模参数模型的性能优势与轻量化部署的实用价值。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/step-3-5-flash\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/step-3-5-flash</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：PaddleOCR-VL-1.5</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"966\" data-imgfileid=\"100017873\" data-ratio=\"0.6037037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7069b4e9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8szmUKA3vvjWgic28s2SIyAEfauoa7BBdrDhrCnUeOnxN6iaakYT16zqo5ZHJEGEouKwE0dxeoM8Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★PaddleOCR-VL-1.5是PaddleOCR-VL的下一代高级模型，在OmniDocBench v1.5上实现了94.5%的新一代最高精度。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型通过Real5-OmniDocBench基准测试评估了其在真实世界物理失真（如扫描伪影、倾斜、扭曲、屏幕摄影和照明）下的鲁棒性。实验结果表明，该模型在新策划的基准测试中达到了SOTA性能。此外，模型还扩展了印章识别和文本定位任务，同时保持了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">0.9B超紧凑VLM</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的高效性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/paddleocr-vl\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/paddleocr-vl</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：Thinker</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"769\" data-imgfileid=\"100017874\" data-ratio=\"0.48055555555555557\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0afd005a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8szmUKA3vvjWgic28s2SIyZp1MvMcGzxxFGwibI8uG0fGw5cBOQBT0ojiaJVnVhzFe7GNRPolgvdZQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Thinker是一个专为体现智能而设计的先进视觉语言基础模型。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">传统的视觉语言模型常常在视角混淆和时间忽视方面存在不足，而Thinker通过高质量的数据集策划、多阶段训练和强化学习，弥合了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">通用场景理解</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">与</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">机器人任务级能力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">之间的差距。它在任务规划、空间智能、时间理解和视觉定位四个核心维度上展现了先进的能力，并在7个体现AI基准测试中创下新纪录，显著超越现有的开源、闭源和专业基线，展示了其作为体现智能和自主机器人决策基础的潜力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/thinker\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/thinker</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">④项目：AlignXplorePlus</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"501\" data-imgfileid=\"100017872\" data-ratio=\"0.31296296296296294\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2bc7d9a7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8szmUKA3vvjWgic28s2SIyDcaJVib0FBzbiagxR0XIbbgx834KSbgiab18sQDmwOtwU9IbdGibYWiaGfA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★AlignXplorePlus是一个用于大语言模型的可迁移个性化框架。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目基于AlignXplore进行改进，提出了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">自然语言</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">可以作为表达用户偏好的通用接口的理念。AlignXplorePlus能够从社交网络、电商平台和新闻流等异构来源推断出高质量的用户偏好总结，并展示了在任务和模型之间的强迁移能力。该框架支持从</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">流输入</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">中进行偏好推理，并在噪声或不完美信号下保持稳定性能，确保在动态环境中的可靠个性化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/alignxploreplus\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/alignxploreplus</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Earth2Studio</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"1022\" data-imgfileid=\"100017876\" data-ratio=\"0.6388888888888888\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ff188fe1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8szmUKA3vvjWgic28s2SIyCdabbcW0krwhtHbkJnJ8AZicib906mxpsiczZ1fFkUAmPZpSNoUPRpicoQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Earth2Studio是一个基于Python的开源软件包，旨在帮助用户快速使用AI地球系统模型。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">其使命是让每个人都能构建、研究和探索由AI驱动的天气和气候科学。Earth2Studio提供了一个AI推理流水线工具包，专注于天气和气候应用，能够在不同的AI框架、模型架构、数据源和科学机器学习工具上运行，并提供统一的API。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/earth2studio\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/earth2studio</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：VL-LN</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"1127\" data-imgfileid=\"100017877\" data-ratio=\"0.7046296296296296\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=22cde334&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8szmUKA3vvjWgic28s2SIyuO398p0icWfibFduHZQibRDegDWhneIo4AQiciaxBwMaFXdiaZQYIwBq0jicg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★VL-LN是一个基准测试平台，提供了大规模自动生成的数据集和全面的评估协议，用于训练和评估支持对话的导航模型。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目旨在推动长期目标导向的导航研究，通过主动对话提升导航模型的性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/vl-ln\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/vl-ln</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇总了 2026 年 2 月初发布的六项前沿开源 AI 项目，涵盖高性能大模型 Step-3.5-Flash、高精度 OCR、具身智能、个性化框架及气候科学工具。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文汇总了 2026 年 2 月初发布的六项前沿开源 AI 项目，涵盖高性能大模型 Step-3.5-Flash、高精度 OCR、具身智能、个性化框架及气候科学工具。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了近期开源的一系列高质量人工智能项目。核心亮点包括阶跃智能（Stepfun-ai）推出的 Step-3.5-Flash 系列，该模型拥有 199B 参数并提供 FP8/Int4 量化版本，旨在优化大规模模型在多样化硬件上的部署效率。此外，文章还涵盖了在物理失真环境下表现卓越的 PaddleOCR-VL-1.5、专注于机器人决策的具身智能模型 Thinker、LLM 可迁移个性化框架 AlignXplorePlus，以及面向气候科学的 Earth2Studio 和导航基准平台 VL-LN。这些项目展示了 AI 技术在模型压缩、多模态理解、具身智能和交叉学科应用中的最新进展。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Step-3.5-Flash 通过量化技术实现了大规模参数模型的高效部署。",
      "explanation": "该模型在拥有 199B 参数的基础上，利用 FP8 和 Int4 量化优化，显著降低了算力与存储开销，使其能灵活适配多种硬件环境。"
